"It holds students accountable for using their time out of class to travel to their destination, handle the business at hand, and return to class.  It also frees middle school teachers from the responsibility of taking an entire class to the restroom as if they are elementary students. It tracks the location of students all over the building and allows us to use tools to prevent encounters of students who may need to avoid each other in the hallways.  There's so much I have enjoyed about SMARTPASS this school year.  It is an excellent electronic pass system I believe every school would enjoy!"
